<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id748e326a-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s120112"><num value="120112">§ 120112.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of this chapter, the term “State” includes the District of Columbia and the territories and possessions of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id748e326b-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/110/254/s1/a/2">Pub. L. 110–254, § 1(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="2008-06-30">June 30, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/2421">122 Stat. 2421</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
